{"tid":2362770,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"MARVEL STUDIOS總裁透露《死侍3》最新進展","createTime":"2021-01-11T16:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T16:48:47.000Z","uid":105567,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dbae8f1b172bf2a71e0c262382d59e2b8b9da25a","tid":2362770,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:28:19.000Z","msg":"MARVEL STUDIOS總裁Kevin Feige，日前接受傳媒網站Collider訪問時透露了《死侍3》將會繼續是R級（限制級）電影，而且將會設定在MCU世畀之中！<br />\n他透露：「它將被定為R級（限制級）電影，我們現在正在製作劇本，而賴恩&middot;雷諾士 (Ryan Reynolds)現在正在監督劇本，電影今年內不會開拍。Ryan是一位非常忙碌和非常成功的演員。我們已經宣佈了許多要做的事情，令人興奮的是，所有事情已經進入軌道。再說，他將會是MCU中的非常不同角色，Ryan有種特珠能力，看到他將那個角色變成現實真是太棒了。」<br />\n似乎死侍除咗能打破第四面牆，同時都打破了迪士尼電影的限制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://collider.com/deadpool-3-mcu-confirmed-r-rating-filming-details-kevin-feige-interview/?fbclid=IwAR32jb3xMwHPtMWmebCr70rvEB2dK_R2pUGe04PC9FpAjC41UzYo_sp1hxg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcollider.com%2Fdeadpool-3-mcu-confirmed-r-rating-filming-details-kevin-feige-interview%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR32jb3xMwHPtMWmebCr70rvEB2dK_R2pUGe04PC9FpAjC41UzYo_sp1hxg&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=788fe776\" target=\"_blank\">https://collider.com/deadpool-3-mcu-confirmed-r-rating-filming-details-kevin-feige-interview/?fbclid=IwAR32jb3xMwHPtMWmebCr70rvEB2dK_R2pUGe04PC9FpAjC41UzYo_sp1hxg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3XnRt5J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3XnRt5J.jpg&h=13689402&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d2ae8efaa51e0400082162e236f60ec17013be1","tid":2362770,"uid":202354,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:31:23.000Z","msg":"唔會再畀錢睇荷里活電影，上網睇算"},{"pid":"50145be4fdbf93db28b63fe0c95c5cd9daf174a5","tid":2362770,"uid":67454,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:31:56.000Z","msg":"食屎啦荷里活"},{"pid":"599442db64d1ecc1ea5c591be18dc7a0654a7807","tid":2362770,"uid":16109,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy